sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>(KServe / OpenShift Route)
    participant Drogon as Drogon HTTP Server<br/>REST port/TCP
    participant gRPC as gRPC Server<br/>gRPC port/TCP
    participant Handler as HttpRestApiHandler<br/>(API key validation)
    participant MP as MediaPipe Graph Executor
    participant LLM as LLM Calculator<br/>(GenAiServable)
    participant GenAI as OpenVINO GenAI Pipeline<br/>(Continuous Batching)
    participant MM as Model Manager
    participant OV as OpenVINO Runtime<br/>(ModelInstance)
    participant DAG as DAG Scheduler<br/>(EntryNode → DLNode → ExitNode)
    participant CloudSDK as Cloud SDK<br/>(S3/GCS/Azure)
    participant CloudStore as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,CloudStore: Flow 1: REST - OpenAI Chat Completions (Streaming)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>Drogon: Forward request
    Drogon->>Handler: Route to handler
    Handler->>Handler: Validate API key<br/>(if configured)
    Handler->>MP: Dispatch to MediaPipe graph
    MP->>LLM: Execute LLM Calculator
    LLM->>GenAI: Run continuous batching pipeline<br/>(prefix cache, KV cache)
    loop Token Generation (SSE Stream)
        GenAI-->>LLM: Generated token
        LLM-->>MP: Token packet
        MP-->>Drogon: SSE event
        Drogon-->>Client: data: {"choices":[...]}
    end
    Drogon-->>Client: data: [DONE]

    Note over Client,CloudStore: Flow 2: gRPC - KServe v2 Model Inference

    Client->>gRPC: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    gRPC->>MM: KFSInferenceServiceImpl
    MM->>OV: Get ModelInstance<br/>(version routing)
    OV->>OV: OpenVINO infer_request<br/>(CPU/GPU/NPU)
    OV-->>MM: Inference result
    MM-->>gRPC: InferResponse
    gRPC-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client,CloudStore: Flow 3: Model Loading from Cloud Storage

    MM->>MM: Config watcher detects<br/>new/updated model
    MM->>CloudSDK: FileSystem Factory<br/>(detect s3:// gs:// az://)
    CloudSDK->>CloudStore: Download model files<br/>Auth: IAM / SAS / ADC
    CloudStore-->>CloudSDK: Model artifacts
    CloudSDK-->>MM: Local model cache
    MM->>OV: Compile model<br/>(OpenVINO Core)
    OV-->>MM: Model ready

    Note over Client,CloudStore: Flow 4: DAG Pipeline Inference

    Client->>Drogon: POST /v1/models/pipeline:predict
    Drogon->>Handler: Route to handler
    Handler->>DAG: Dispatch to DAG pipeline
    DAG->>DAG: EntryNode → parse input
    loop For each DLNode / CustomNode
        DAG->>OV: DLNode: OpenVINO inference
        OV-->>DAG: Intermediate result
        Note right of DAG: CustomNode: dlopen<br/>shared library
    end
    DAG->>DAG: ExitNode → assemble output
    DAG-->>Drogon: Pipeline result
    Drogon-->>Client: JSON response
